  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nInstead of using individual gauges with a binary value for each validator status (active, exited, slashed, and withdrawable), use a single gauge with a numeric value for each status.  As it is now, there's no easy way to use the provided metrics within Grafana to display each validator's status.\r\n\r\nExample:\r\n```\r\n# HELP validator_statuses validator statuses: 1 PENDING 2 ACTIVE 3 EXITED 4 WITHDRAWABLE 5 SLASHED 6 SLASHED WITHDRAWABLE\r\n# TYPE validator_statuses gauge\r\n```",
